    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Security-Group"><a href="#Security-Group" class="headerlink" title="Security Group"></a>Security Group</h1><ul><li>Associated with instance</li><li>Stateful: allow return traffic</li><li>default rule:<ul><li>allow all out-bound traffic</li><li>deny all in-bound traffic</li></ul></li><li>Only allow traffic defined by explicit rules</li><li>Use cases: controlling access to specific instances (application access)</li></ul><h1 id="Network-ACL"><a href="#Network-ACL" class="headerlink" title="Network ACL"></a>Network ACL</h1><ul><li>Associated with subnets</li><li>Stateless: not allow return traffic</li><li>Default ACL for VPC<ul><li>allow all in-bound and out-bound traffic</li></ul></li><li>Self-defined ACL default:<ul><li>deny all in-bound and out-bound traffic</li></ul></li><li>Use cases: controlling traffic bound of the subnets (network protecting, compliance, traffic control, IP blocking)</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
